name: Etrian Odyssey Untold: The Millennium Girl
description: Etrian Odyssey Untold: The Millennium Girl is a 2013 role-playing video game for the Nintendo 3DS by Atlus. It is part of the Etrian Odyssey series, and is both a "reimagining" and a remake of the first entry. It was released by Atlus in Japan on June 27, 2013, and in North America on October 1, 2013, and released by NIS America in Europe on May 2, 2014. It is available via both Nintendo eShop and retail at release.
